snippet.title: Dance Collider - Trailer
snippet.description:
It's your time to become a dance master and take down Uriel! 
Battle 9 of the best dancers around the globe at their own style of dance. Featuring 45 Songs by F-777 and a VR dance editor. Dance Collider is the ultimate dance and rhythm game.

Available on:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/692690/Dance_Collider
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/1275664972562703
https://www.viveport.com/apps/6c8e8b77-c99a-4044-815a-7aad9c2b655d/Dance_Collider
